Rising Cement Output in South Africa Putting Pressure on Prices, PPC Says

-- B y   S i k o n a t h i   M a n t s h a n t s h a
-- 
2011-07-14T09:02:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-14/rising-cement-output-in-south-africa-putting-pressure-on-prices-ppc-says.html
South Africa  is producing more
cement than it’s consuming and this is putting pressure on
prices, Kevin Odendaal, Pretoria Portland Cement Co.’s executive
for corporate stategy, told reporters in Pretoria today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
